sentences.sentence: FITOW moved WNW in the past 24 hours with slight weakening.
sentences.translation: 菲特于过去24小时向西北偏西移动并稍为减弱。

sentences.sentence: At 20 HKT, SINLAKU was centred about 330 km (180 NM) WNW of Okinawa.
sentences.translation: 在20 HKT，森垃克集结在冲绳岛之西北偏西约330公里(180海里)。

sentences.sentence: It is expected that 10w will track WNW in the southern periphery of this ridge towards Guangdong.
sentences.translation: 在这个副高的引导下，预料10w将向西北偏西移动，趋向广东沿岸。
